      <title>Sam Altman 支持的 Rain AI 聘请苹果芯片老手领导硬件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/sam-altman-backed-rain-ai-hires-apple-chip-vet-to-lead-hardware</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rain AI 已聘请苹果公司一位芯片高管来领导硬件工程，这是本月试图设计新型人工智能半导体的初创公司第二次高调招聘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/sam-altman-backed-rain-ai-hires-apple-chip-vet-to-lead-hardware</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银在海外融资 18.6 亿美元，加大对人工智能的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/softbank-raises-1-86-billion-overseas-as-it-boosts-ai-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团公司通过发行美元和欧元债券筹集了约 18.6 亿美元，这是自 2021 年以来的首次外币债务交易，这家日本科技公司正采取行动启动对人工智能的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/softbank-raises-1-86-billion-overseas-as-it-boosts-ai-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:11:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SK 集团经历 20 年来最大并购潮，即将迎来重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/biggest-shakeup-in-two-decades-looms-for-sk-after-deals-spree</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SK 公司面临着一个问题：在斥资 210 亿美元进行收购后，这家韩国第二大企业集团的规模变得过于庞大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/biggest-shakeup-in-two-decades-looms-for-sk-after-deals-spree</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 00:44:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>腾讯借助热门游戏成为中国市值增幅最大的游戏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/tencent-rides-hit-game-for-china-s-biggest-gain-in-market-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一款热门的新网络游戏重新激发了投资者对腾讯控股有限公司的乐观情绪，推动了中国股市在 2024 年最大的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/tencent-rides-hit-game-for-china-s-biggest-gain-in-market-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 00:15:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据美国联邦通信委员会的新规定，监狱电话费率将大幅降低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/prison-phone-rates-set-for-drastic-reduction-under-new-fcc-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦通信委员会已提出新规，降低囚犯的电话和视频通话费率，此举可能会极大地重塑 ViaPath Technologies 和 Aventiv Technologies 等监狱电信提供商的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/prison-phone-rates-set-for-drastic-reduction-under-new-fcc-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 22:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uber、Lyft 与马萨诸塞州就司机福利达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uber-lyft-reach-agreement-with-massachusetts-on-driver-benefits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优步技术公司 (Uber Technologies Inc.) 和来福车公司 (Lyft Inc.) 就一系列员工福利达成一致，以解决马萨诸塞州一项长期存在的州诉讼，该诉讼质疑司机作为独立承包商的就业身份，从而阻止了两家公司在 11 月将此问题提交选民审议的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uber-lyft-reach-agreement-with-massachusetts-on-driver-benefits</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 21:46:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软告知更多客户俄罗斯黑客查看了电子邮件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/microsoft-tells-some-clients-that-russian-hackers-viewed-emails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司正在通知更多客户，他们与这家科技巨头之间的电子邮件交流遭到俄罗斯黑客攻击，这一迹象表明，之前报道的由政府支持的入侵事件的影响比最初想象的更为广泛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/microsoft-tells-some-clients-that-russian-hackers-viewed-emails</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 21:22:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊推迟发射柯伊伯宽带卫星计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/amazon-delays-launch-of-project-kuiper-broadband-satellites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司表示，预计将于今年第四季度发射首批太空互联网卫星，此前该公司曾表示最早将于上半年发射。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/amazon-delays-launch-of-project-kuiper-broadband-satellites</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 18:06:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>空气炸锅、自助晒黑机：警方缴获网上盗窃的赃物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/california-police-seize-suspected-stolen-goods-bound-for-amazon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方突袭了南加州的一个仓库，仓库里堆满了价值约 200 万美元的疑似被盗商品，警方表示，这些商品很可能最终流入亚马逊公司和其他零售商运营的在线市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/california-police-seize-suspected-stolen-goods-bound-for-amazon</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:24:41 GMT</pubDate>
